{"title_page": "Warri", "text_new": "{{About|the Nigerian city|the Caribbean game|Oware|the steamship|SS Warri}}\n{{more citations needed|date=August 2014}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use British English|date=September 2010}}\n<!-- Infobox begins -->\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|settlement_type        = City\n|image_skyline          =\n|imagesize              = 300px\n|image_caption          = Street in Warri\n|image_flag             =\n|flag_size              =\n|image_seal             =\n|seal_size              =\n|image_shield           =\n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_type      =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|nickname         =   Waffi City, Waffi Town \n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_map              =\n|mapsize                =\n|map_caption            =\n|image_map1             =\n|mapsize1               =America\n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = Nigeria<!-- the name of a location map as per http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Location_map -->\n|pushpin_label_position =bottom\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location in Nigeria\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n|coordinates            = {{coord|5|31|N|5|45|E|region:NG|display=inline}}\n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = [[File:Flag of Nigeria.svg|25px]] [[Nigeria]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[States of Nigeria|State]]\n|subdivision_type2      =Local Government\n|subdivision_type4      =\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Delta State]]\n|subdivision_name2      =[[Warri South|Warri South LGA]], [[Warri South West|Warri South West LGA]]\n|subdivision_name4      =\n<!-- Politics ----------------->\n|established_title      =  <!-- Settled -->\n|established_date       =\n|established_title2     =  <!-- Incorporated (town) -->\n|established_date2      =\n|established_title3    